summary: Nord female. Lara-Croft-style ripoff or something.
descriptionHtml:
UPD: added savegame from very beginning so you can use this character from level one.
UPD2: She\'s even looks better with \"No more blocky faces\", \"better lips\" and \"better eyes\" mods.

This is my first upload so don\'t judge mo to hard =)
So to be honest i think i\'ve managed to create one of the cutes characters( without mods ofc) in Skyrim and i want to share it with you guys. Her name is Lara and she\'s a bounty hunter of 23 lvl. 
Her main skills:
Dualwield
Light Armor
Sneaking

So basically she is some kind of contract killer who\'s interested in wealth and don\'t care too much about other people.

I\'ve tryed to avoid a lot of quests in the game and spent the most of the time just running around and doing random quests(To be honets this is how TES games meant to be played IMHO ). I\'ve done about 3-5 quests in the main storyline, about 7+ quests for The Dark Brotherhood and about 4 quests for the theif guild. I\'ve never bought any houses, got married, used any companions. 

Bonus: I hide all my stuff in Delphia\'s secret place in Riverwood
author: Venomus
